    "body": "Hello Cython community. I wanted to take a stab at [this issue](https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/3696) as it looks like it hasn't ben addressed yet. Hoping the build CI passes and if not someone can point me in the right direction perhaps? Tried running tests locally but got a syntax error from `Shadow.py`",
