            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "It doesn't look like these are ever used in the test.\n\nAt very least I think we'd want to know from the tests that Cython is calling `+=` rather than `_ = _ + _`.\n\nNote that I don't think you can usefully use the return value because `a = (b += 2)` isn't valid Python code (although is valid c++ code)",
